description: Spreading happiness one delicious, fluffy, authentic Hawaiian shaved ice at a time!Winner 2012 Toast of Music City "Best Food Truck" 3rd Place!We have a passion for serving only the best authentic Hawaiian shaved ice. This starts with ice BLOCKS made with filtered water. If you don't see a block, it's not really shaved ice! We then hand craft our own flavors using 100% cane sugar. Nor corn syrup here! Come give us a try! Contact us about private events or if you'd like us at your location. No event is too big or too small!
name: Blue Monkey Shaved Ice
